title: Entry list: The 2017 Supercars Championship
text:
Supercars: The full entry list for the 2017 Virgin Australia Supercars Championship March 2, 2017 7:12pm @willdale956 Source: FOX SPORTS THE full Virgin Australia Supercars Championship field has been locked in for the 2017 season, with 26 cars to take to the track for the opening round of the championship at the Clipsal 500 Adelaide. 
There is a combined 7,041 Supercars race starts among the 26 drivers on the grid, ranging from veteran Craig Lowndes with 610 down to 16-year-old rookie Alex Rullo who will make his main game debut this weekend.
